<p><a name="Eponym" id="Eponym"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Claude_Debussy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Eponym">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Eponym</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Asteroid" title="Asteroid">Asteroid</a> <a href="/wiki/4492_Debussy" title="4492 Debussy">4492 Debussy</a>, discovered in 1988, is named for Claude Debussy.</li>
</ul>
